This also lended itself to the film noir vibe to go along with all the detective work the audience wasâ€¦

The movie not-so-elegantly broaches the topic of nostalgia. Is it productive to spend present energy on the past? Is it pointless to appreciate an art, technology or culture that has been rendered obsolete? As someone whose record player shares a room with 55â€ television with a sound bar, I find myself wondering those same questions in my own life.Â
